00:12:55.440 --> 00:13:00.860
of products because it's a
kind of huge buzz, in all of foods in general,

00:13:00.860 --> 00:13:05.070
um, I mean in our downtown location we make
a lot of vegan foods

00:13:05.070 --> 00:13:10.890
as well in the salty section of the store,
